<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>АгроСкоринг — Умный Кабинет Фермера</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Unbounded:wght@300;400;600;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:#080d0b;--bg2:#0d1710;--surface:#152019;--surface2:#1e2e24;
  --border:#263d2e;--accent:#4ade80;--accent2:#86efac;--accent3:#bbf7d0;
  --gold:#fbbf24;--red:#f87171;--orange:#fb923c;--blue:#60a5fa;
  --text:#e2f0e7;--text2:#8db89a;--text3:#4e7a5c;
  --mono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;--display:'Unbounded',sans-serif;--body:'Noto Sans',sans-serif;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--body);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;
  background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(74,222,128,.025) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(74,222,128,.025) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:44px 44px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(8,13,11,.93);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 28px}
.nav-logo{font-family:var(--display);font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.12em}
.nav-steps{display:flex;gap:2px}
.nav-step{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:5px 12px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;
  transition:all .2s;font-size:10px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--text3);border:1px solid transparent;white-space:nowrap}
.nav-step:hover{color:var(--text2);background:var(--surface)}
.nav-step.active{color:var(--accent);background:rgba(74,222,128,.07);border-color:rgba(74,222,128,.18)}
.nav-step.done{color:var(--accent2)}
.step-num{width:17px;height:17px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--surface2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:9px;font-weight:700}
.nav-step.active .step-num{background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg)}
.nav-step.done .step-num{background:var(--accent2);color:var(--bg)}
.page{display:none;min-height:100vh;padding-top:56px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.page.active{display:block}
.container{max-width:840px;margin:0 auto;padding:44px 22px}
.progress-line{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:36px;animation:fadeUp .4s ease both}
.prog-step{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;flex:1;position:relative}
.prog-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--border);margin-bottom:5px;position:relative;z-index:1;transition:all .3s}
.prog-step.done .prog-dot{background:var(--accent)}
.prog-step.active .prog-dot{background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(74,222,128,.18)}
.prog-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
.prog-step.done .prog-label,.prog-step.active .prog-label{color:var(--accent2)}
.prog-step::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:4px;left:-50%;right:50%;height:1px;background:var(--border)}
.prog-step:first-child::before{display:none}
.prog-step.done::before{background:var(--accent)}
.page-header{margin-bottom:36px;animation:fadeUp .5s ease both}
.page-tag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.page-tag::before{content:'';display:block;width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--accent)}
.page-title{font-family:var(--display);font-size:clamp(20px,3.5vw,30px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:8px}
.page-sub{color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;line-height:1.65}
.card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:22px;margin-bottom:14px;animation:fadeUp .5s ease both}
.card-title{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.form-row{display:grid;gap:10px;margin-bottom:10px}
.c2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.c3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr}
.field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
label{font-size:10px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--text2);letter-spacing:.05em}
input,select{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;color:var(--text);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;padding:9px 13px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;width:100%;-webkit-appearance:none}
input:focus,select:focus{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(74,222,128,.09)}
input.filled{color:var(--accent2);border-color:rgba(74,222,128,.28);background:rgba(74,222,128,.03)}
.fnote{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:var(--mono)}
.fnote.ok{color:var(--accent)}.fnote.warn{color:var(--orange)}.fnote.err{color:var(--red)}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:7px;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--display);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.05em;transition:all .2s;text-transform:uppercase}
.btn-primary{background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg)}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--accent2);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 8px 22px rgba(74,222,128,.22)}
.btn-secondary{background:var(--surface2);color:var(--text2);border:1px solid var(--border)}
.btn-secondary:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.btn-danger{background:rgba(248,113,113,.1);color:var(--red);border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,.3)}
.alert{padding:11px 14px;border-radius:7px;font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;gap:9px;align-items:flex-start}
.a-warn{background:rgba(251,146,60,.07);border:1px solid rgba(251,146,60,.28);color:var(--orange)}
.a-ok{background:rgba(74,222,128,.05);border:1px solid rgba(74,222,128,.22);color:var(--accent2)}
.a-err{background:rgba(248,113,113,.07);border:1px solid rgba(248,113,113,.28);color:var(--red)}
.a-info{background:rgba(96,165,250,.06);border:1px solid rgba(96,165,250,.22);color:var(--blue)}
.a-fraud{background:rgba(248,113,113,.12);border:2px solid rgba(248,113,113,.5);color:var(--red);font-weight:600}
.check-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:11px;padding:13px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;transition:opacity .15s}
.check-item:last-child{border:none}
.check-item:hover{opacity:.85}
.checkbox{width:19px;height:19px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .2s}
.check-item.req-item .checkbox{border-color:var(--orange)}
.check-item.checked .checkbox{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent)}
.check-label{flex:1}
.check-name{font-size:12px;margin-bottom:2px}
.check-desc{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:var(--mono)}
.check-pts{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);white-space:nowrap;margin-top:2px}
.check-item.checked .check-pts{color:var(--accent)}
.req-tag{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--orange);background:rgba(251,146,60,.1);border:1px solid rgba(251,146,60,.25);border-radius:3px;padding:1px 5px;margin-left:6px;letter-spacing:.06em}
.score-ring-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:28px;padding:22px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;margin-bottom:18px;animation:fadeUp .4s ease both}
.score-ring{position:relative;width:96px;height:96px;flex-shrink:0}
.score-ring svg{transform:rotate(-90deg)}
.score-ring-text{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.score-num{font-family:var(--display);font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);line-height:1}
.score-max{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--text3)}
.score-breakdown{flex:1}
.score-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(38,61,46,.5)}
.score-row:last-child{border:none}
.score-label{color:var(--text2);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px}
.score-val{font-family:var(--display);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)}
.score-bar-wrap{height:2px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;margin-top:3px}
.score-bar{height:100%;background:var(--accent);border-radius:2px;transition:width .8s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1)}
.type-grid{display:grid;gap:9px;margin-bottom:18px}
.g3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.g2{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
.type-card{padding:14px;background:var(--bg2);border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;text-align:center}
.type-card:hover{border-color:rgba(74,222,128,.5);background:rgba(74,222,128,.03)}
.type-card.selected{border-color:var(--accent);background:rgba(74,222,128,.07)}
.type-icon{font-size:22px;margin-bottom:7px}
.type-name{font-size:10px;font-weight:500;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--text2);line-height:1.4}
.type-card.selected .type-name{color:var(--accent)}
.animal-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono)}
.animal-table th{text-align:left;padding:7px 11px;color:var(--text3);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.animal-table td{padding:9px 11px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(38,61,46,.4)}
.animal-table tr:last-child td{border:none}
.s-ok{color:var(--accent)}.s-warn{color:var(--orange)}.s-err{color:var(--red)}
.result-hero{text-align:center;padding:36px 22px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(74,222,128,.07),rgba(74,222,128,.015));border:1px solid rgba(74,222,128,.18);border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:22px;animation:fadeUp .6s ease both}
.result-badge{display:inline-block;padding:5px 14px;background:rgba(74,222,128,.1);border:1px solid rgba(74,222,128,.28);border-radius:100px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase}
.result-score{font-family:var(--display);font-size:68px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);line-height:1;margin-bottom:6px}
.result-score-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:14px}
.result-status{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--accent2)}
.shortlist-card{padding:18px 20px;background:rgba(251,191,36,.05);border:1px solid rgba(251,191,36,.2);border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:8px}
.shortlist-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:12px}
.rank-num{font-family:var(--display);font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold)}
.rank-title{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:2px}
.rank-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:var(--mono)}
.why-title{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
.why-item{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px;font-size:12px;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(38,61,46,.4)}
.why-item:last-child{border:none}
.why-pts{font-family:var(--display);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0}
.factor-card{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:14px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;margin-bottom:7px;animation:fadeUp .5s ease both}
.factor-icon{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:7px;background:rgba(74,222,128,.09);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;font-size:17px}
.factor-info{flex:1}
.factor-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:3px}
.factor-desc{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:var(--mono)}
.factor-pts{font-family:var(--display);font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0}
.ai-box{padding:13px 15px;background:rgba(74,222,128,.03);border-left:3px solid var(--accent);border-radius:0 7px 7px 0;margin-top:14px;font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--accent2);line-height:1.65}
.ai-label{font-size:9px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:5px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase}
.divider{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:18px 0}
.bottom-bar{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding-top:22px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:28px}
.qm-label{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:6px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.07em}
.qm-outer{height:8px;background:var(--surface2);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.qm-inner{height:100%;border-radius:4px;transition:width .7s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1),background .5s}
.qm-ticks{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:4px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--text3)}
.qm-grade{font-family:var(--display);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;margin-top:6px}
.fraud-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.78);z-index:999;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;backdrop-filter:blur(6px)}
.fraud-modal{background:var(--surface);border:2px solid var(--red);border-radius:14px;padding:32px;max-width:420px;width:90%;text-align:center}
.fraud-icon{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:14px}
.fraud-title{font-family:var(--display);font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:10px}
.fraud-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:20px;font-family:var(--mono);text-align:left}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@media(max-width:600px){
  .c2,.c3{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .g3{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  nav{padding:0 14px}
  .nav-step .step-text{display:none}
  .container{padding:28px 14px}
  .result-score{font-size:52px}
  .score-ring-wrap{flex-direction:column;text-align:center}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">АГ·РО·СКОР</div>
  <div class="nav-steps">
    <div class="nav-step active" id="nav1" onclick="goPage(1)"><div class="step-num">1</div><span class="step-text">Профиль</span></div>
    <div class="nav-step" id="nav2" onclick="goPage(2)"><div class="step-num">2</div><span class="step-text">Аудит</span></div>
    <div class="nav-step" id="nav3" onclick="goPage(3)"><div class="step-num">3</div><span class="step-text">Заявка</span></div>
    <div class="nav-step" id="nav4" onclick="goPage(4)"><div class="step-num">4</div><span class="step-text">Shortlist</span></div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- FRAUD MODAL -->
<div class="fraud-overlay" id="fraud-overlay" style="display:none">
  <div class="fraud-modal">
    <div class="fraud-icon">🚨</div>
    <div class="fraud-title">АНОМАЛИЯ ОБНАРУЖЕНА</div>
    <div class="fraud-desc" id="fraud-desc"></div>
    <button class="btn btn-danger" onclick="document.getElementById('fraud-overlay').style.display='none'">Понятно — исправить заявку</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 1 -->
<div class="page active" id="page1">
<div class="container">
  <div class="progress-line">
    <div class="prog-step active"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Профиль</div></div>
    <div class="prog-step"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Аудит</div></div>
    <div class="prog-step"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Заявка</div></div>
    <div class="prog-step"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Shortlist</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-tag">Страница 01</div>
    <div class="page-title">Авто-профиль и<br>Наличие земель</div>
    <div class="page-sub">Вход через ЭЦП (ИИН/БИН). Данные из ГБД ЮЛ и ИСЕГКН подтягиваются автоматически. Hard Filter: земли = 0 → скор 0.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="animation-delay:.08s">
    <div class="card-title">🔐 Авторизация через ЭЦП</div>
    <div class="form-row c2">
      <div class="field">
        <label>ИИН / БИН (12 цифр)</label>
        <input type="text" id="iin" placeholder="000000000000" maxlength="12" oninput="onIin(this)">
        <div class="fnote" id="iin-note">Ключ для связи ГБД ЮЛ · ИСЕГКН · ИСЖ · КГД</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Тип участника</label>
        <select id="entity-type">
          <option value="">— выберите —</option>
          <option value="kfh">КФХ (Крестьянское хозяйство)</option>
          <option value="ip">ИП</option>
          <option value="too">ТОО / АО</option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="loadProfile()" style="margin-top:6px">
      <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
      Авторизоваться и загрузить данные
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="card" id="profile-card" style="display:none;animation-delay:.12s">
    <div class="card-title">👤 Профиль хозяйства (ГБД ЮЛ)</div>
    <div class="form-row c2">
      <div class="field"><label>Наименование хозяйства</label><input type="text" id="farm-name" class="filled" readonly></div>
      <div class="field"><label>ОКЭД</label><input type="text" id="oked" class="filled" readonly></div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row c2">
      <div class="field"><label>Область</label><input type="text" id="region" class="filled" readonly></div>
      <div class="field"><label>Район</label><input type="text" id="district" class="filled" readonly></div>
    </div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="card-title">🗂 Земельный блок (ИСЕГКН) — Hard Filter</div>
    <div class="form-row c3">
      <div class="field"><label>Кадастровый номер</label><input type="text" id="cadastre" class="filled" readonly></div>
      <div class="field"><label>Общая площадь (га)</label><input type="text" id="land-total" class="filled" readonly></div>
      <div class="field"><label>Пастбища (га)</label><input type="text" id="land-pasture" class="filled" readonly></div>
    </div>
    <div id="land-alert"></div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="card-title">🐄 Поголовье (ИСЖ)</div>
    <div class="form-row c3">
      <div class="field"><label>КРС всего (голов)</label><input type="text" id="cattle-total" class="filled" readonly></div>
      <div class="field"><label>в т.ч. коровы (голов)</label><input type="text" id="cows-total" class="filled" readonly></div>
      <div class="field"><label>МРС (голов)</label><input type="text" id="sheep-total" class="filled" readonly></div>
    </div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="card-title">💳 Банковские реквизиты (для выплаты)</div>
    <div class="form-row c2">
      <div class="field"><label>ИИК (счёт)</label><input type="text" id="bank-iik" placeholder="KZ00 0000 0000 0000 0000"></div>
      <div class="field"><label>БИК банка</label><input type="text" id="bank-bik" placeholder="KCJBKZKX"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bottom-bar" id="p1-bottom" style="display:none">
    <div></div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="goPage(2)">Далее: Аудит инфраструктуры →</button>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 2 -->
<div class="page" id="page2">
<div class="container">
  <div class="progress-line">
    <div class="prog-step done"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Профиль</div></div>
    <div class="prog-step active"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Аудит</div></div>
    <div class="prog-step"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Заявка</div></div>
    <div class="prog-step"><div class="prog-dot"></div><div class="prog-label">Shortlist</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="page-tag">Страница 02</div>
    <div class="page-title">Аудит инфраструктуры<br>(Приложение 5, стр. 113)</div>
    <div class="page-sub">Отметьте мощности хозяйства. Инфраструктурный балл — ключевой Merit-фактор скоринга.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="score-ring-wrap">
